snippet.title: This is Narrowboat Simulator Version 1.9
snippet.description:
This video demonstrates the Narrowboat Simulator 1.9 featuring  new "canal content" around the Pontcysyllte Aqueduct.

Please visit the games homepage for more information:
https://sites.google.com/view/narrowboat-simulator

Music:
"Princess", by Josh Woodward: https://www.joshwoodward.com/song/Princess (cc-by 4.0)
"Learn To Fly" (Instrumental), by Josh Woodward: https://www.joshwoodward.com/song/LearnToFly (cc-by 4.0)

Credits for materials used in the game:
https://sites.google.com/view/narrowboat-simulator/about/credits
